      "body" : "Somehow these screenshots tell more than lots of text. In my (also MacOS) case IntelliJ created a project structure with only <code>&#47;data&#47;res</code> in Classpath tab, and removing/reinserting Android 4.3 Platform, it as in the screenshot above, resolved the issue of unrecognized android dependencies."
