    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Once I have followed all these steps, I start to receive error messages in all android classes calls like:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/avcLu.png\" alt=\"Cannot resolve Android Classes\"></p>\n\n<p>I revolved that including android.jar in the SDKs Platform Settings:</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/UampT.png\" alt=\"SKDs Classpath\"></p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2262457,
      "reputation" : 734,
      "user_id" : 1992152,
      "user_type" : "registered",
